// 標準命令.  wade 整理於 7/6/1996
=========================================================================
[溝通用指令]    重要喔, 至少要會跟別人溝通.
  ask  reply  say  semote  song  tell  tune  followup  post

[探險用指令]    除了溝通之外, 最最基本的命令
  brief  buy  close  drink  drop  eat fill  follow  get  give  go
  light  lock  look  open  put  search  team  unlight  unlock

[查詢用指令]    學會查詢跟自己相關的重要資料是生存最大的利器
  date  finger  functions  guild  help  hp  id  ident  inventory
  query  quests  score  skills  time  uptime  who  wizlist

[戰鬥與技能]    戰鬥跟技能, 是玩泥巴的重要特色
  abandon  apprentice  cast  cmd  conjure  enable  enchant  enforce
  exercise  exert  expell  fight  flee  kill  learn  meditate  perform
  pkla  practice  recruit  remove  respirate  surrender  unwield
  scribe  study  wear  wield  wimpy  wimpydir

[個人用命令]	多知道一些, 總是有利於生存的
  alias  auc  bet  describe  do  gage  hell  ident  nick  passwd
  quit save  secure  set  sig  suicide  to  unsecure  unset
